      ],
      "start": 9.84,
      "text": "It is currently 13 degrees and raining in Berlin-Tempelhof."
    },
    {
      "end": 17.96,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 15.8,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "aa3c8a35747"
      ],
      "end": 32.12,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3"
      ],
      "start": 18.6,
      "text": "NVIDIA is simplifying how administrators secure high performance networking for AI clusters. The company introduced intent based security profiles within its Unified Fabric Manager for Quantum InfiniBand."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "aa3c8a35747"
      ],
      "end": 45.36,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s4",
        "s5"
      ],
      "start": 32.28,
      "text": "Network managers can now auto configure multi tenant fabric security in a single click. The system uses three specific profiles: General, Bare Metal Cloud, and Secured Bare Metal Cloud."
    },
    {
      "end": 57.76,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 46.5,
      "text": "This change reduces deployment time from days or hours down to minutes. It lowers the operational overhead required to secure inference infrastructure in shared AI environments."
    },
    {
      "end": 61.06,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s8"
      ],
      "start": 59.14,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 63.92,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 61.06,
      "text": "This afternoon will be cloudy with temperatures between 15 and 16 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 69.36,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 67.96,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 70.24,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
